highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Me Porto Bonito” is the highest at #3.
“Romantic Homicide” by d4vd is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 80 spots at #44.
“Forget Me” by Lewis Capaldi is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #57.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 293 weeks straight.
